title: Affordable, Spacious & Unbeatable 3 BR Apartment Home
posting_body: ['Make our community your new home!', 'Located in Cottage Grove, The Legends is Minnesota’s all-new premier 55+ independent living community!', 'We have paid attention to every detail and are offering smart layouts, quality materials, and luxurious amenities seldom found in this price range.', 'You will immediately notice the exceptional design and first-class finishes.', 'The apartments are spacious; the amenities include an in-home washer and dryer and a private balcony or patio (most homes).', 'Plus, the community amenities are tough to beat with beautifully appointed community spaces, including a community room, fitness center, craft/card room and beauty salon.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Separate Dining & Living Room Areas', '- Ample Storage & Countertop Space', '- On-Site Theater Room & Beauty Salon', '- Heated Underground Parking Garage ($80/month)', '- 24-Hour Fitness Center', '- Close To Tons Of Shopping, Dining & Entertainment Options!', '- Active 55+ Senior Living Community!', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Our community is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to schedule your tour:', 'show contact info', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'GajsAT8Ef']
